trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see langword="My.Application.Startup" /> event.
trans-unit.target: 提供 <see langword="My.Application.Startup" /> 事件的資料。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ApplicationServices.WindowsFormsApplicationBase.Startup> event occurs when the application starts, if the application implements the Visual Basic Application Model.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ApplicationServices.WindowsFormsApplicationBase.Startup>事件發生時應用程式啟動時，如果應用程式實作 Visual Basic 應用程式模型。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Overview of the Visual Basic Application Model](~/docs/visual-basic/developing-apps/development-with-my/overview-of-the-visual-basic-application-model.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[Visual Basic 應用程式模型概觀](~/docs/visual-basic/developing-apps/development-with-my/overview-of-the-visual-basic-application-model.md)。

trans-unit.source: <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ApplicationServices.StartupEventArgs> contains the command-line arguments of the application and indicates whether the application startup should be canceled.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ApplicationServices.StartupEventArgs> 包含應用程式的命令列引數，並指出是否應取消應用程式啟動。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection`1" /> object that contains the command-line arguments of the application.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection`1" /> 物件，包含應用程式的命令列引數。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ApplicationServices.StartupEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ApplicationServices.StartupEventArgs" /> 類別的新執行個體。
